<guidelines>
**Initial planning (v1.0):**
- Phase count depends on granularity setting (coarse: 3-5, standard: 5-8, fine: 8-12)
- Each phase delivers something coherent
- Phases can have 1+ plans (split if >3 tasks or multiple subsystems)
